        "body": "<p>Check <a href=\"https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/elasticsearch/docs/current/reference/html/#elasticsearch.mapping.meta-model.annotations\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">the documentation<\/a> for the <code>@Field<\/code> annotation, it has a <code>name<\/code> parameter:<\/p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>@Field(name = &quot;@timestamp&quot;, type = FieldType.Date)\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
